data.title: Atelier / Bespoke Costume
data.text:
The production of costumes is one of our most beautiful tasks. We fulfill every costume wish – from the development to the professional realization – gladly in cooperation with you.

Our costumes and accessories owe their longevity to loving restoration and refurbishment by our team. We employ designers and costume makers, custom tailors, fashion and wardrobe assistants.

In our workshop, we combine traditional crafts with the fast pace of industry. And if the process needs to be even quicker, we can also manufacture for you on set.

In the unlikely case that we are not able to fulfill a request, we call on the assistance of our network of milliners, shoemakers, plasterer and model makers.
